DescriptionAuthorScreenshotsCSS code <p>Use <code>order</code> values below 0 to move specific buttons to the left of the non-ordered buttons, and values above 1 to move them to the right of the non-ordered buttons.</p> <p> </p> <pre><code>/* [Global changes] Change the order of navigation bar buttons */

nav .navbar-nav:first-child {
display: flex;
flex-direction: row;
}
div.nav-link[data-rb-event-key="/tags"] {
order: -2;
}
div.nav-link[data-rb-event-key="/groups"] {
order: -1;
}
div.nav-link[data-rb-event-key="/scenes"] {
order: 1;
}
</code></pre>

